The paper discusses open access publishing in the fields of software engineering and information systems, which are subfields of computer science. The paper also analyzes a sample of open access journals in these fields, which suggests that the paper may be relevant to the digital libraries (cs.DL) sub-category. Additionally, the paper proposes an analysis framework for open access journals, which could be relevant to the software engineering (cs.SE), information retrieval (cs.IR), cryptography and security (cs.CR), and cybernetics (cs.CY) sub-categories.
